{"tid":610003,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"(求飛黃牛免進) 五月天人生無限公司無限放大版(5)","createTime":"2018-03-29T13:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T12:46:39.000Z","uid":75832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"a947812a2ed244e844bf42ca976c86ee7ece3be2","tid":610003,"uid":75832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:44:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個post係討論買飛/演唱會相關資訊<br />\n求飛自己出返去開post啦 thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lfug2yzt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flfug2yzt&h=56257ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五月天 人生無限公司 無限放大版<br />\n演出日期: 2018年5月4,5,6,11,12,13日 (共6場)<br />\n<br />\n門票價錢: HK$1180 / $880 / $680(坐位及企位) / $480<br />\n演出場館: 香港迪士尼樂園 露天場地<br />\n<br />\n優先購票: 2018年3月19日9am起 (東亞信用卡)<br />\n優先訂票網址: <a href=\"http://www.aegticketing.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aegticketing.com&d=fQOv7zOkaCBnn8N6nq7najCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=48734480\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aegticketing.com</a><br />\n優先訂票熱線: (852) 28 611 611 (上午9時至晚上9時)<br />\n<br />\n公開發售: 2018年3月29日10am起 購票通 Cityline<br />\n方法1) 網上購票: <a href=\"http://www.cityline.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cityline.com%2F&d=fQOv7zOkaCBnn8N6nq7najCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9565e79b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cityline.com/</a><br />\n方法2) 電話購票: 2111 5333<br />\n方法3) 門市購票: 通利琴行及其他售票處<br />\n<br />\n座位表<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3duv98pi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3duv98pi&h=2747a86b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n場地位置圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/45cqeg8d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhollan